fore being blended and bottled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;What\'s in the box:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;x 1 1.5 Litre Anthonij Rupert Protea Rose&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Features:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;- Appealing pale coral hue&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;- Crisp, and dry, and with a peppery finish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Nimbus Sans L&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-fami